Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've come from Lieseltania.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very pleased to meet you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you should've at least\Nsent me word that you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But His Majesty promised me\Ntickets to the Phoenix Festa,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in exchange for not saying\Na word to you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True to form, he's just\Na bit too fond of mischief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it was my big brother\Nwho put you up to wearing that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! He said if I wore this,\Nyou'd know me right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... I don't believe that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this is what I normally\Nwear, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A maid's uniform? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flora's working\Nas a maid-in-waiting at the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually she's still just a trainee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But I never would've guessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:26.39,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Corrupt Ruler
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That you've been fighting for the sake\Nof an orphanage, Riessfeld-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I-It's really not all that big a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know. Tell us, Flora...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was Julis like back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I'd just like to know, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's more or less the same\Nas she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever she was with us,\Nshe was so kind and warm-hearted,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and when she was at the palace,\Nshe was dashing and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So she's the same as she is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.39,0:03:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are my memories of the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was a nun who wanted to preserve\Nmemories as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to her influence, the kids got\Ninto the habit of taking pictures, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flora, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's me getting my hair washed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see? Did you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You saw, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I didn't! I didn't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flora, how many times\Nhave I told you to delete that photo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... but... that's one of my\Nprecious memories of you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flora, you really adore Julis, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I really look up to Her Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And someday I plan to come here\Nas a student myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'm gonna help everyone\Nin the orphanage, just like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you there's no need\Nfor you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But! But! I want to do something\Nto help everybody, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're still just a child. Don't worry\Nabout such things, you should be—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the student council president\Nat Jie Long is even younger than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why not me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It will be at least two years\Nbefore you're old enough to enroll here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By then, I'll have already\Nfulfilled all your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you the last time\NI saw you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That I'd save you all, no matter what,\Nand change that country myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in order to do that,\NI'm going to win all of the Festas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you have so little faith in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course that's not the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Riessfeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your goals are lofty and epic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But sadly, you're out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:05:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, we're going to win\Nthe Phoenix Festa. Right, Kirin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not going to lose, either!\NBecause I have a wish I can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Sasamiya and Lady Toudou...\Nyou're my princess's rivals, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rivals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yabuki's not back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your older sister... what about her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems like he's seen another person\Nwielding that same Ogre Lux.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Oh, Mr. Amagiri!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Good evening, Priscilla.\NSorry to call you out of the blue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Oh, no, that's perfectly fine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I was thinking\Nthat I needed to thank you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}but since the Phoenix Festa is still\Ngoing on, I didn't want to bother you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}But thank you very much\Nfor the other day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, I haven't done anything\Nyou should thank me for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}You brought my sister\Nback to me, Mr. Amagiri.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can never thank you enough for that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I know! Would it be all right\Nif I asked you to dinner again—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}All right, enough! Just let me talk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}W-Wait a second!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yo, Amagiri.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Irene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You wanted to talk to me,\Nnot Priscilla, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, that's not right, either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not me that you really\Nwant to talk to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's that bastard Dirk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}No, I'm just repeating\Nwhat I heard that damned Dirk say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}He told me that you'd be\Ncalling me sooner or later,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}wanting to get in touch with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then could you give him\Na message from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him that I want to ask him\Nabout Haruka Amagiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd like to meet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure thing. All part of my job, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I owe you one. Thanks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}But you'd better watch your back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}We're not the only ones\Nhe's got at his beck and call.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rumor has it that Erenshkigal herself\Nworks for him, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Erenshkigal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And also...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's got Grimalkin\Nin his clutches as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grimalkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}That's Rewolf's\Nintelligence organization.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Those guys are seriously hard core.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Just give them the order,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and they'll do any kind of dirty work\Nwithout a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gotcha. I'll be vigilant, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}You do that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}There's no point\Nunless you still have your life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the way, I saw your match today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Man, you were toiling!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Serves you right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}E-Excuse me, Amagiri!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Would you mind waiting for a second?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Hey! Hey, what's the big idea?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}You're going to thank him\Nproperly, remember?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}You don't have to tell me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A-Amagiri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... Uh, let's see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just thought I should\Nthank you myself, see?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But don't read too much into it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know, for that thing.\NThe Gravi-Sheath thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not that I want to admit it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but since you busted it, I'm barely\Nearning anything, and it's awful...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, if it wasn't for you,\Nthe fact is, I'd be a goner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, is that what you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}You saved me. Thanks, man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now the ball's\Nin the Tyrant's court, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I haven't been home in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yabuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, my bad. Did I wake you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, long time no see, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the Phoenix Festa\Nis a profitable time for me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, by the way,\NI saw your match yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So now you're into\Nthe quarterfinals. Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}DELICIOUS TEA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though it did feel like a hollow victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, you still managed\Nto win, so it's all good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So who are your next opponents,\Nthe Jie Long twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are gonna be a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, their personalities\Ncouldn't be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen their match data,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it sure seems like they have a knack\Nfor hitting you where it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those two really know how to take\Nadvantage of Star Senjutsu, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet their opponents just hate\Ngoing up against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take advantage of Star Senjutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, you've never\Ngone up against Taoists, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}JIE LONG
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the short answer is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that Star Senjutsu takes\Nthe power of a Strega or a Dante
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and generalizes it\Nas a technique, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's more common to see Stregas\Nand Dantes use distinctive powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but then they lose stability,\Nand it's easier to mount a counter-attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Taoists have\Nno such vulnerabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank goodness. So you're awake?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Actually... Flora insists\Non inviting you to lunch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Apparently there's something\Nshe just has to ask you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Flora?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Needless to say,\Nas long as you don't mind...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, that's totally fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Really? Then if you don't mind,\Ncan you come out to the Business District?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}The thing is, it's horribly\Ncrowded along Main Street.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}We should probably\Nmeet up somewhere else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, what's this?\NLooking for a place to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then I'll be happy\Nto recommend a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is a date, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}D-Date? Y-You moron!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't get the wrong idea! Flora's the one\Nwho has some business with Ayato,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and it's not like I want to see him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}See? Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, listen to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Not a lot of tourists,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and the atmosphere and the food\Naren't bad. A well-kept secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:11.71,Broadast,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A stylish hidden café in a quiet neighborhood\NRice omelet and parfait are recommended!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm impressed\Nthat you knew this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What do you think, Julis?\NWant to meet up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I guess so.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Although it's annoying that it was\NYabuki who recommended it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All right, then that's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's meet up in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yabuki. I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because after all, having you owe me one\Nis sure to come in handy sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to pray\Nthat it doesn't cost me too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Really, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's ketchup\Nall over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but the atmosphere\Nand the food are quite good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it,\Nbut Yabuki gave us good information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell that to him yourself.\NHe'll be thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will do no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to grief many times,\Nthanks to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a long way\Nto go to offset that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So... what is it\Nyou wanted to ask me, Flora?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your jumbo parfait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, do you want one of those, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your jumbo parfait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:12:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking\Nthat you're surprisingly soft on kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's not often that these kids\Nget the chance to be spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, at the orphanage\Nthey rarely get to have such sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once in a while shouldn't hurt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've been sending us money,\Nit's been a lot easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The nuns said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're sending them money?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no big deal, really. It's my\Nbonus money for being a Page One.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not like there's anything\NI could spend it on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness! Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open up and say ah, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is quite tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I feel like my\Ntongue's gonna melt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it, let me\Noffer you some, too, Mr. Amagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean I can have some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The princess and the nuns always say
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that good food tastes\Neven better when you share it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, th-that's certainly true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you see, that spoon...\NI myself just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here you go!\NSay ah, Mr. Amagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! This really\Ntastes great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Julis, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Flora, what about those\Nquestions you wanted to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this done and over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... Now we're finally\Ngetting down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What was the first thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here's my first question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how far have you gone in your\Nrelationship with the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:15:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What kind of question is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That question... you didn't\Nthink it up yourself, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His Highness told me\Nto investigate the boy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who might become his\Nyounger brother in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confiscating this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a job I was entrusted with!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me see it through to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denied!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you when you're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could I speak to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're Ayato Amagiri, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you, but I wonder\Nif you could come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!\NI still haven't introduced myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the secretary to the student council\Npresident at Rewolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Korona Kashimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the president awaits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does the Tyrant\Nwant with my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold up, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm the one\Nwho asked for this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis and Flora, you wait here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. I'm coming\Nwith you to this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're partners, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? B-But it's just Mr. Amagiri\Nthat the president wishes—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}That's fine with me.\NBring them over, Korona.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I might as well take this opportunity\Nto see the Glühen Rose in person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}V-Very well, understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Flora, I'm sorry, but there it is. You can\Nget back to the hotel on your own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Murakumo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure look absentminded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If someone like you is their Rank #1,\NSeidoukan's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who it was\Nthat gave the order
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to destroy such an absentminded\Nopponent... Tyrant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard, you've got a lot of nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, I heard\NIrene Urzaiz say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- That you... Ayato!\N- Julis, it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Irene only told us\Nbecause it was a one-time thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, we have to let it go,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or we'll only make trouble for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see your wits, at least,\Nare reasonably quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that has nothing to do\Nwith what I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But before we start talking,\Nlet me warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not obligated\Nto answer your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just be sure to keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... If that's the case,\Nwhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...\Nlet's just call it a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A busy student council president\Nlike you is acting on a whim?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I can\Nprovide you with, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want something,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you have to offer something yourself,\Nor no deals can be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you pass.\NWhat did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My sister... Haruka Amagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you know about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it's not as if I know\Nall that much about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've only ever seen her once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Eclipse Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about it, Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was created by scumbags\Ndissatisfied with the Festas,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who wanted something\Nmore violent and stimulating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An illegal battle game with no rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The matches are decided when one\Nof the players either loses consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,loses his or her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it had a fervent following\Namong some wealthy patrons,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it thrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, they did away\Nwith the Eclipse Festa years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because the captain of the Guard\Nreally couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw Haruka Amagiri,\Nit was as a contestant of that Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying...\Nthat my sister took part in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I remember it well because she was\Nusing the damned Ser=Versta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And... how did that match end?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka Amagiri lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah... Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hear that she didn't actually die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I know\Nwhat became of her afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one and only time\NI ever saw Haruka Amagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now it's my turn\Nto ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you...\Nwhat's Madiath Mesa to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Madiath Mesa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Chairman\Nof the Festa Steering Committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like you're\Nplaying dumb there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're done talking.\NNow get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one thing\NI can't figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just how did you find out\Nwhere we were?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We only decided to go to that café\Nonly a few hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could understand\Nif we'd made a reservation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but on such short notice, how...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm under no obligation to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when I went to pick up Mr. Amagiri\Nand Ms. Riessfeld,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there was an adorable\Nlittle girl with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, she looked just like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who she was?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's not listed in the data\Nyou gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she's still quite small,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and she wasn't wearing\Na school emblem,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't think\Nshe's an Asterisk student.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one more thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She even had on a maid's\Nuniform, that little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it? A maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really became her! She was adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me more about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-Time for guard duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the true heroine's\Ntime to shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:40.00,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 15\NBreaking the Memory Barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, no, of course\NI wasn't sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is my hour,\Nso there'll be plenty of...
